{
  "id": "RAW_f4aa94",
  "title": "腾讯开源 HunyuanVideo-I2V 图生视频模型+LoRA 训练脚本，社区部署、推理实战教程来啦！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/6IXjk3ERJVCh_X2Q-AJwvw",
  "date": "2025-03-07 11:35:33",
  "author": "魔搭ModelScope社区",
